  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Safe Educational Trails for Kids and Teachers</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Hands-on education in the rainforest is an important part of our &quot;training centre.&quot; We now include elementary school children in our environmental education programme. But in order to take teachers, and especially children, into our forest, it is imperative that we have adequate trails.  We need to build trails where children can walk into the different ecosystems without difficulty and in a safe manner, so that they have an overall positive experience.</narrative>
  </description>
